Package: gustave
Type: Package
Title: A User-Oriented Statistical Toolkit for Analytical Variance Estimation
Depends:
  R (>=3.3.3)
Imports:
  Matrix,
  methods,
  stats,
  MASS
Suggests:
  testthat,
  sampling,
  vardpoor,
  magrittr
Version: 0.3.0
Author: person("Martin", "Chevalier", "martin.chevalier@insee.fr", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Martin Chevalier <martin.chevalier@insee.fr>
Description: 
  Provides a toolkit for analytical variance estimation in survey sampling. Apart from 
  the implementation of standard variance estimators (Sen-Yates-Grundy, Deville-Till√©), 
  its main feature is to help the methodologist produce easy-to-use variance estimation 
  "wrappers", where systematic operations (linearization, domain estimation) are handled 
  in a consistent and transparent way for the end user.
License: GPL-3
